description:
With a sweater-knit outer face combined with an easy-care fleece interior, the Better Sweater Jacket functions as a superb insulating piece in backcountry settings and urban environments. Not bulky, so it layers well under a shell. The high collar buffers you from gusts of cold air, with a zipper garage to protect your skin when it's zipped to the top.Polyester fabric has sweater-knit face, fleeced interior.Dyed with a process that reduces energy, water and dyestuffs.Full zip with a wind-blocking stand-up collar.Flatseam construction reduces bulk and helps eliminate chafing.Raglan sleeves are comfortable under packstraps.Zippered chest pocket and handwarmer pockets.Micropolyester jersey trim at cuffs and bottom hem holds its shape well.

